Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.render

Class Render

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.render.Render
  • public class Render
extends java.lang.Object
    Main Render Module class. Simply stores the Drawing panels and performs updates to both every tick. States: - 0: Intro State - 1: Main Menu - 2: Level Select - 3: Pause - 4: Main Game State - 5: You Died State - 6: Win State - 7: Game Information
